  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt; 18 years

          -  Indication to a knee or hip arthroplasty under general anesthesia

          -  Sinusal rhythm

        Non Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women

          -  Black skin

          -  Dialysis

          -  Cardiac arrythmia

          -  Sepsis

          -  Use of another hemodynamic monitoring during surgery
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
